room_title: Escape room "Shipwrecked" by Escape Room Entertainment in Melbourne
room_address: 630 S Wickham Rd, Suite 105 Melbourne, FL 32904
room_description: On a sunny afternoon, you and your mates are sailing the Caribbean Sea. Suddenly, a storm rolls in and your boat is swept onto a deserted island. While you are searching for any sign of life you come upon a shipwreck. On further inspection, you realize it’s a pirate’s ship! You and your mates go inside to investigate and the galley door slams shut behind you. You and your mates have 60 minutes to escape. Can you open the galley door before the ghost of Captain Silver appears?
